OL,3,CSchool secretaries and caretakers
OL,4,Cbegin indefinite strike
OL,6,FSchool secretaries and caretakers are
OL,7,Fto begin indefinite strike action on
OL,8,FThursday.
OL,10,FThey are campaigning for 2,600 school
OL,11,Fstaff to be included in the public
OL,12,Fservice pension scheme and other
OL,13,Fentitlements.
OL,15,FThe industrial action kicks in as
OL,16,Fthousands of schools prepare for the
OL,17,Freturn of the academic year.
