OL,3,CSchool secretaries and caretakers
OL,4,Cbegin indefinite strike
OL,6,FThe first day of the strike action
OL,7,Fwill involve a rally of school
OL,8,Fsecretaries and caretakers at the
OL,9,FDepartment of Public Expenditure's
OL,10,Foffices in Dublin on Thursday.
OL,12,FMr Pike said: "Our members are
OL,13,Fbeginning this strike today because,
OL,14,Fdespite decades of service, thousands
OL,15,Fof school secretaries and caretakers
OL,16,Fstill face the prospect of retiring
OL,17,Fwith no pension.
