OL,3,CSchool secretaries and caretakers
OL,4,Cbegin indefinite strike
OL,6,F"The State's continued refusal to give
OL,7,Fthem the same employment status as
OL,8,Ftheir colleagues has locked out
OL,9,Fseveral generations of school staff
OL,10,Ffrom secure income in retirement.
OL,12,F"The policy is a calculated policy
OL,13,Fdecision to maintain inequality."
OL,15,FThe chair of Forsa's School
OL,16,FSecretaries branch, Luisa Carty, said
OL,17,Fschool secretaries and caretakers are
OL,18,Femployed under identical arrangements
OL,19,Fto teachers and special needs
OL,20,Fassistants.
