OL,3,CSchool secretaries and caretakers
OL,4,Cbegin indefinite strike
OL,6,F"They are appointed by boards of
OL,7,Fmanagement, paid through the
OL,8,FDepartment of Education, and their
OL,9,Fterms are set by the Minister for
OL,10,FEducation.
OL,12,F"Despite these arrangements we
OL,13,Fcontinue to be denied access to the
OL,14,Fpublic service pension scheme, as well
OL,15,Fas the same occupational sick pay and
OL,16,Fbereavement leave schemes.
