OL,3,CSchool secretaries and caretakers
OL,4,Cbegin indefinite strike
OL,6,F"It makes no sense. Our school
OL,7,Fsecretary colleagues in Education and
OL,8,FTraining Board schools have full
OL,9,Fpublic service status, including
OL,10,Fpension access. We are striking for
OL,11,Ffairness," she said.
OL,13,FOn Friday, a series of rallies around
OL,14,Fthe country are planned to be held at
OL,15,F11am, including at the Department of
OL,16,FEducation, Taoiseach Micheal Martin's
OL,17,FCork constituency office and Tanaiste
OL,18,FSimon Harris' constituency office in
OL,19,FBray.
